OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy with the chance of some light
OL,7,Frain to start, but soon becoming dry
OL,8,Fand largely clear through the evening
OL,9,Fand overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FIt will stay dry with good
OL,12,Fbright or sunny spells through Friday.
OL,13,FLight winds through the day will
OL,14,Ffreshen somewhat in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
